ing some existing extensions, we will also show that a new setup\ninvolving a master equation of a random walk with suitable chosen transition\nrates in the photon reciprocal space furnishes not only Kompaneets equation but\nalso a first generalization to a system of bosons under a possible driving.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jul 2021 18:24:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-19"}
