 which 30\\% will be reflected back again on\nthe gold plating of the wires. Thus we can observe 74% of the total S2 light.\nCompared to a dual-phase detector, however, we do not suffer from the\nextraction efficiency, sometimes reported as low as 50%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 09:58:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
