alibrated parameters have been used to simulate different trajectories.\nOverall, the paper shows the importance of cross-fertilization between traffic\nflow and vehicle studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 11:37:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-19"}
