tions performed on the model\nshow good agreement with the analytic predictions. The simplicity of the model\npromises that real-world systems can be found which display the dynamics\ninduced by correlated/uncorrelated disorder.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 13:36:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 15:04:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-30"}
